<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5643832006210811424">Melanie Benjamin is the author of the New York Times bestselling novels THE SWANS OF FIFTH AVENUE and THE AVIATOR&apos;S WIFE, as well as the national bestseller ALICE I HAVE BEEN, and THE AUTOBIOGRAPHY OF MRS. TOM THUMB and MISTRESS OF THE RITZ. Her most recent novel is the new historical fiction, THE CHILDREN&apos;S BLIZZARD, about the real-life devastating blizzard that swept the Great Plains in 1888, up</span>
  <span id="freeText5643832006210811424" style="display:none">Melanie Benjamin is the author of the New York Times bestselling novels THE SWANS OF FIFTH AVENUE and THE AVIATOR'S WIFE, as well as the national bestseller ALICE I HAVE BEEN, and THE AUTOBIOGRAPHY OF MRS. TOM THUMB and MISTRESS OF THE RITZ. Her most recent novel is the new historical fiction, THE CHILDREN'S BLIZZARD, about the real-life devastating blizzard that swept the Great Plains in 1888, upending the lives of the immigrant homesteaders, especially schoolchildren and their young teachers. </span>
  <a data-text-id="5643832006210811424" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

